FBIS3-17505 "drsov059_r_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 27 Mar 1994 Azerbaijan Reinforcements Massed in Fizuli NC2703182194 Baku Radio Baku Network in Azeri 1700 GMT 27 Mar 94 NC2703182194 Baku Radio Baku Network Language: Azeri Article Type:BFN ["Text" of Azerbaijan Ministry of Defense press service communique of 27 March] [Text] Our towns along the Armenian border have been continuously fired on for three days now. [words indistinct] and the enemy has been observed to mass reinforcements and armored units in Fizulinskiy Rayon. Azerbaijan's positions in that area were fired on with various types of arms yesterday. Azerbaijan military units have been taking the necessary measures to strengthen their defensive lines and silence the enemy fire emplacements. The situation in the other parts of the front line has been relatively peaceful.
